<h2>Your verification code</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>Enter this code to sign in to <%= Rails.configuration.x.app.name %>:</p>

<div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; padding: 16px; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <%= @code %>
</div>

<p>This code expires in 10 minutes.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
